Package controller

Class SearchViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.SearchViewController

  • public class SearchViewController
extends java.lang.Object
    This controller handles the search results window, that is opened and loaded when a user searches for either a date range or some photo tags. It controls viewing photos in the results, creating an album from the results, and slideshow of the results.
    Author:
    Brian Schillaci

      • updateAlbumDateRange

        private static void updateAlbumDateRange​(Album a,
                                         Photo newPhoto)
        This method updates the date range of photos associtated with the album argument passed in. If a photo is added and the Album's start or end dates are null, they are set to the photo object's last modified date.
        Parameters:
        a - - the album the date is to be updated to
        newPhoto - - this is set to the photo object being copied to the new album created its date range is then modified
